import React from 'react';

import img1 from './Treasure-hunt.jpeg';
import './Card.css';

import { CardColumns,CardGroup,Card,Button,Container,Nav,Navbar,NavDropdown } from 'react-bootstrap';
import 'bootstrap/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css';

const MyCards = (props) => {

  return(

    <Container className='mt-5' fluid="md">

      <CardGroup className='customRounded'>
        <CardColumns className='customRounded'>
          <Card className='customRounded'>
            <Card.Img variant="top" src={img1} alt="Logo" />
            <Card.Body>
              <Card.Title>Card title</Card.Title>
              <Card.Text>
                This is a wider card with supporting text below as a natural lead-in to
                additional content. This content is a little bit longer.
              </Card.Text>
            </Card.Body>
            <Card.Footer>
              <Button>Enter</Button>
            </Card.Footer>
          </Card>
          <Card>
          <Card.Img variant="top" src={img1} alt="Logo" />
            <Card.Body>
              <Card.Title>Card title</Card.Title>
              <Card.Text>
                This card has supporting text below as a natural lead-in to additional
                content.{' '}
              </Card.Text>
            </Card.Body>
            <Card.Footer>
              <Button>Enter</Button>
            </Card.Footer>
          </Card>
          <Card>
          <Card.Img variant="top" src={img1} alt="Logo" />
            <Card.Body>
              <Card.Title>Card title</Card.Title>
              <Card.Text>
                This is a wider card with supporting text below as a natural lead-in to
                additional content. This card has even longer content than the first to
                show that equal height action.
              </Card.Text>
            </Card.Body>
            <Card.Footer>
              <Button>Enter</Button>
            </Card.Footer>
          </Card>
          </CardColumns>
      </CardGroup>

    </Container>


  );


};

export default MyCards;
